Developer Terms of Use
des: Welcome to the Muslim Community. This skill can help you by providing the time table for daily prayer. let this skill know which city or country you want the prayer time table for. For example, if you want to know the prayer time table for new york, then simply say, 'I am interested in New York'. And, if you want to know the qibla direction for New York, then say, 'Give me the qibla direction for New York' or If you want to know more options, then say, help!
